      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'How to play the game:


    A customer will come in and ask for a specific
    drink (Like on the left). It''s your job to find the correct glass, assemble
    all the ingredients, add ice if needed, then mix it all together.


    The game
    is controlled by a series of "Clocks" (See Right). Each clock is split into segments,
    and each segment has its own action. When you press [SPACE] the action for whichever
    segment the hand of the clock is in will activate. In the example on the right,
    if you pressed space now, the action in the right segment would activate.


    [Press
    Space to continue]

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a8b2e1ee89c5095479f4b519db5f33a5, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -3265695042867483017, guid: a8b2e1ee89c5095479f4b519db5f33a5, type: 2}
