  m_text: 'Before you get stuck in, choose what level of difficulty you''d like the
    game to be:


    Casual- No time limit, just enjoy making some drinks.


    Balanced-
    You only get a set amount of time to make each drink or the customer won''t be
    happy.


    Challenging- Like balanced, but less time to make your drinks, and
    each time you have to reset your drink you lose time!'
