      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Congratulations on your new position as bartender aboard the ISB; The
    international space bar. \n\nOur diplomats are hosting visitors from the outer
    galaxies, and it is your job to keep them refreshed between meetings, giving
    them a taste of the best beverages earth has to offer.\n\nWe have provided you
    with all the ingredients, glassware, and recipes you'll need, so go out there
    and make earth proud.\n\n[Press Space to continue]"
